description: [``botocore``] Support StorageField and custom displays for data-bound options in form builder. Support non-string operands for predicates in collections. Support choosing client to get token from.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling
[``botocore``] This release updates the value of MaxResults.
[``botocore``] C6in, M6in, M6idn, R6in and R6idn bare metal instances are powered by 3rd Generation Intel Xeon Scalable processors and offer up to 200 Gbps of network bandwidth.
[``botocore``] Updated public documentation for the Describe and Tagging APIs.
[``botocore``] Update sagemaker-runtime client to latest version
[``botocore``] Amazon SageMaker Asynchronous Inference now allows customer's to receive failure model responses in S3 and receive success/failure model responses in SNS notifications.
[``botocore``] This release rolls back association config feature for webACLs that protect CloudFront protections.
